{"tid":632230,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"聯想集團(00992.HK)楊元慶：營業額達三年來最高 最艱難日子已過去","createTime":"2018-04-17T07:51:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T11:01:00.000Z","uid":106204,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c3e4d37acec5045a7816e8544f873fa08edd265b","tid":632230,"uid":106204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:51:58.000Z","msg":"聯想集團(<a href=\"http://00992.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00992.HK&d=u%2BkFq2YMDkcNMG79MupW%2BNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=44114873\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00992.HK</a>)董事長楊元慶出席聯想誓師大會時表示，在過去一年聯想營業額重拾增長，並達到三年來最高，相信最艱難的日子已經過去，並再一次進入上升的通道。<br />\n<br />\n他指出2018/19財年公司要全面擁抱智能化，在個人電腦方面要繼續保持領先的盈利能力，移動業務需積極求進，數據中心業務期望實現可持續的盈利增長，並期望在人工智能方面打造新的競爭優勢。<br />\n<br />\n他又為集團訂下五個目標，包括新型智能設備營業額達10億美元，軟件和服務總營業額達到20億美元，PC增值服務滲透率今明兩年各提升1個百分點，超大規模數據中心業務營業額達到15億美元，並冀透過利用工業IoT和大數據技術，令智能化解決方案的營業額和客戶數各增長3倍。(el/u) ~<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c3cc0a892a2fa7499bd8581a426356d930cb7e","tid":632230,"uid":106204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600f6b6498705377a160e333a68ec67e55df8f53","tid":632230,"uid":57424,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:53:25.000Z","msg":"隻野跌到佢傻左, 係時候出黎出口術<br />\n等緊 3.2入"},{"pid":"d665a13d034378d8695a5781a463c1afa7a30fd8","tid":632230,"uid":106204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:53:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"928622c6252017b28bf80988ea4947aaa3462c72","tid":632230,"uid":106204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T08:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abade82a0cc4ebce2556f56f1cab9ca40